<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Memo – Curry</title><link>http://forest0923.github.io/memo/en/docs/lang/curry/</link><description>Recent content in Curry on Memo</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><atom:link href="http://forest0923.github.io/memo/en/docs/lang/curry/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Docs: Install Curry</title><link>http://forest0923.github.io/memo/en/docs/lang/curry/install/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>http://forest0923.github.io/memo/en/docs/lang/curry/install/</guid><description>
&lt;p>Curry is a language that has features of both functional and logic programming languages. PAKCS is an interpreter that can execute programs written in Curry. PAKCS converts Curry code into Prolog and executes it.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="install">Install&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul class="nav nav-tabs" id="tabs-0" role="tablist">&lt;li class="nav-item">
&lt;a class="nav-link active"
id="tabs-00-00-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#tabs-00-00" role="tab"
aria-controls="tabs-00-00" aria-selected="false">Arch&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li class="nav-item">
&lt;a class="nav-link"
id="tabs-00-01-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#tabs-00-01" role="tab"
aria-controls="tabs-00-01" aria-selected="false">Ubuntu&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="tab-content" id="tabs-0-content">&lt;div class="tab-pane fade show active"
id="tabs-00-00" role="tabpanel" aria-labelled-by="tabs-00-00-tab">
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>```sh
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>paru -S pakcs
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>```&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="tab-pane fade"
id="tabs-00-01" role="tabpanel" aria-labelled-by="tabs-00-01-tab">
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>```sh
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo apt-add-repository ppa:swi-prolog/stable
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo apt update
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo apt install swi-prolog
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo apt install pakcs
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>```&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://www.informatik.uni-kiel.de/~pakcs/download.html">download site&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="basic-usage">Basic Usage&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Sample program:&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-haskell" data-lang="haskell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#999;font-style:italic">-- family.curry&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">data&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">Person&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">Alice&lt;/span> | &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">Bob&lt;/span> | &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">Charlie&lt;/span> | &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">Dave&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#447fcf">parent&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">Alice&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">True&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#447fcf">parent&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">Bob&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">True&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#447fcf">child&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">Charlie&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">True&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#447fcf">child&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">Dave&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">True&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#447fcf">parent_child&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">Alice&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">Charlie&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">True&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#447fcf">parent_child&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">Alice&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">Dave&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">True&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#447fcf">parent_child&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">Bob&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">Charlie&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">True&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#447fcf">parent_child&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">Bob&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">Dave&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">True&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#447fcf">sibling&lt;/span> x y &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">=&lt;/span> parent_child z x &amp;amp; parent_child z y
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold">where&lt;/span> z free
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Enter interactive shell with &lt;code>pakcs&lt;/code>:&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ pakcs
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>which: no rlwrap in (/usr/local/bin:/usr/local/sbin:/usr/bin:/usr/bin/site_perl:/usr/bin/vendor_perl:/usr/bin/core_perl)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt; /home/user/.pakcsrc installed.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> __ _
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>|_ \ | | PAKCS - the Portland Aachen Kiel Curry System
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> \ \ | |____
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> / \| ____| Version 3.3.0 of 2021-02-15 (swi 8.2)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> / /\ \ |
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>/_/ \_\| (using Curry Package Manager, version 3.0.0)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Type &amp;#34;:h&amp;#34; for help (contact: pakcs@curry-lang.org)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Prelude&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Load files:&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Prelude&amp;gt; :l family
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Test:&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>family&amp;gt; parent Alice
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>True
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>family&amp;gt; child Dave
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>True
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>family&amp;gt; parent_child Bob Charlie
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>True
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>family&amp;gt; sibling Charlie Dave
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>True
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>True
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>family&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;blockquote>
